---
title: Korean Beef Bibimbap with Black Sesame Rice & Garlic Aioli
description: Bibimbap literally translates to “mixed rice” in Korean. This traditional dish can be made with almost any ingredients, but always starts with a bed of rice and a medley of sautéed veggies. A perfectly fried egg tops it all off in a spectacular fashion!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/korean-beef-bibimbap-dc354fd7.jpg
